::'''Wen Shiling:''' So, Special Assistant (Trailblazer), your mission is to assist me in completing multiple projects efficiently and safely during this time and compiling them into reports!
::'''Wen Shiling:''' Don't worry, you just need to collect experimental samples and supplies for me. Just leave the rest of the research work to me!
::'''Wen Shiling:''' Ahem, that being said, let's get down to brass tacks.
::'''Wen Shiling:''' The first round of experiments mainly revolves around the "Voidranger: Tramplers" of the "Antimatter Legion." The research title shall be named... Let me think... It shall be named "A Brief Analysis of Force Distribution on Quadruped Tramplers."
